  div.row
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
      h2.h1.text-justify
        'What is Petrol Finder?
    div.col-md-1
  div.row
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
      div.text-justify
        'Petrol Finder uses the map provided by <a href=”http://openstreetmap.org/”> Open Srreet Map </a> for displaying the petrol pumps where the fuel is going to be distributed for the certain lots of vehicles for specific dates. The list of petrol pumps is provided by Nepal Oil Corporation and can be viewed <a href='http://nepaloil.com.np/news-events/Notice/5/'> here.</a>
    div.col-md-1
  p
  div.row
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
      h2.text-justify
        'Why?
    div.col-md-1
  div.row
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
      div.text-justify
        'Currently, Nepal is facing a huge humanitarian crisis due to economic blockade at the southern custom points. There is a complete shortage of fuel.  The fuel crisis has made the lives of the people of Nepal very hard.  People from Kathmandu are forced to buy wood to cook food due to the lack of the cooking gas/Liquified Petroleum Gas (LPG) cylinders.
    div.col-md-1
  p
  div.row
    div.col-md-2.col-xs-1
    div.col-md-8.col-xs-10
      div.hidden-xs.hidden-sm
        div#pieChart cost-pie-chart-one=""
      div.visible-xs.visible-sm
        div.text-center
          h3.h4 Average Monthly Spending of Every Household of Five to Cook Food in 2003
        div#pie1
          div#tooltip2 class="hidden"
            p <strong>Expenditure: NRS <span style="color: rgb(0,128,128)" id = "value"> x</span></strong>
        div.pull-right
          em
            small Source: Amrit M Nakarmi, Professor, Tribhuvan University <br/>
    div.col-md-2.col-xs-1
  p
  div.row
    div.col-md-2.col-xs-1
    div.col-md-8.col-xs-10
      div.hidden-xs.hidden-sm
        div#pieChart cost-pie-chart-two=""
      div.visible-xs.visible-sm
        div.text-center
          h3.h4 Average Monthly Spending of Every Household of Five to Cook Food in 2015
        div#pie2
          div#tooltip2 class="hidden"
            p <strong>Expenditure: NRS <span style="color: rgb(0,128,128)" id = "value"> x</span></strong>
        div.pull-right
          em
            small Source: Amrit M Nakarmi, Professor, Tribhuvan University <br/>
    div.col-md-2.col-xs-1
  p
  div.row
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
      div.pull-left
        'The economic blockade has increased expenses for the people. The costs of making food have also increased thanks to the skyrocketing inflation and the economic blockade which is evident from the pie chart comparing the cost of making food between 2003 and 2015 .This blockade comes at the time when Nepal is just recovering from the disastrous earthquakes that struck Nepal on April and June.
    div.col-md-1
  p
  div.row
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
    div.pull-left
      small <em>The Geojson data for the petrol pumps can be downloaded from Nepal Portal's<a href="https://github.com/LKhadka/Nepal-Portal/tree/master/public"> GitHub</a> page.</em>
  div.col-md-1
